query: SELECT p.id, p.name, COUNT(r.id) as reviewCount FROM products p LEFT JOIN reviews r ON p.id = r.productId WHERE p.slug LIKE '%zodiac%' OR p.slug LIKE '%guardian%' OR p.categoryId IN (SELECT id FROM categories WHERE slug LIKE '%zodiac%' OR slug LIKE '%guardian%') GROUP BY p.id, p.name ORDER BY p.id LIMIT 20;
